E[X|X \le c]
 = \int\limits_{0}^{c} x \ p(x|x\le c) \ dx \ + \ 0  = \int\limits_{0}^{c} x \frac{p(x,x\le c)}{p(x\le c)} dx   = \int\limits_{0}^{c} x \frac{p(x)}{p(x\le c)} dx 
p(x,x \le c) = p(x) \ in \ [0,c]
X \le c
